According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal has a 2014 [[impact factor]] of 2.878.<ref name=WoS>{{cite book |year=2015 |chapter=World Neurosurgery |title=2014 Journal Citation Reports |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |edition=Science |series=[[Web of Science]]}}</ref>

